title: 170 - Live From Woodstock '99
description: Today’s episode features a full crew on this fine Friday, as the show is guided by Ty Schmit. All the boys open up with an update on the latest of their media consumption as Mitt is back with Outer Banks, Connor watched the Billie Elish doc. as Tony has watched everything under the sun. The boys then jump into the Pod FOD, which is a folder compiled of things found all over the internet. This weeks FOD includes reactions to the Mathew Vaughn’s Netflix”Spy Thriller” announcement, monkey battles in Japan, which root beer reigns superior, and much more. Nick takes us back to Woodstock ’99 for some Friday Bangerrs to close off the show. Make sure to subscribe to youtube.come/thepodpmi to watch full episodes and don't forget to send your submissions for the Pod FOD to @ThePodPMI on twitter and instagram. We appreciate you rocking with us and we'll see you Wednesday, Cheers.
